General Requirements: 
 Security: The system must be secure, unauthorized access must be prevented, and user data must be protected.
 User-Friendly Interface: An interface that users can easily use and understand must be provided.
 Modularity: The system must be flexible for new devices or functions that may be added in the future.
 Remote Access: Remote access solutions such as mobile applications or web interfaces must be provided so that users can control the system outside of the home.
 Power Consumption and Efficiency: The system must be energy efficient and the power consumption of constantly operating devices must be kept low.

Hardware Requirements:
 Sensors:
  Motion sensors 
  Temperature and humidity sensors
  Door/window sensors (open/closed status)
 Devices:
  Smart plugs and switches
  Motorized curtains
  Smart locks
  Sound systems, smart TVs and other media devices
